  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I assumed, well, while he was listening to my story and feeling sort of like duly [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you know, show, showing that he was feeling for my losses et cetera-- probably had his own.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he was interested more in my hand.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I moved my hand nearer to his part of the body which I didn't want to touch and was near enough.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In the middle of talking, without interrupting the talk, I took it back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I pretended that nothing happened because you can, cannot afford to make any enemies or bad friends in such situations.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he soon cut the talk short, went away, I didn't see him again except once.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "After three weeks, he said, you better leave because an SS doctor is coming.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And not many people leave the hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Most go right away where there is a cure forever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know what it means.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I left.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And ever there was a truth in the saying, from the fire into the, from the frying pan into the fire, that was it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Hardly had I entered my own barracks, I was told to undress because the SS doctor just inspected the people there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Already, there was a line already in front, going to another room which I had never entered because it was probably the private rooms of the block eldest, usually like a couple and mostly like a German criminal.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I haven't, I haven't told you about it yet.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Of course, you must have heard it 100 times when you interview people, they had a green triangle.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There were two different kind of green triangles.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "One point up and one point down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I'm not sure which way-- one of them was the political type of outcast from Germany.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
